1-2 individuals calling in flight from the pond on the southern end of Pool 1 (east side of road). Two individuals took flight upon my approach. The first individual landed at the east side of the pond fairly soon after taking flight from the middle of the north side (first 5-7 calls, I believe). Then, the second individual flew back over the pond and started calling (the remaining calls). It flew back and forth several times before landing about the middle of the north side of the pond. It had been closer to the northwest corner of the pond.
